results.name: Number of 5's in the last section of the set of partitions of n.
comment: Zero together with the first differences of A024789. Also number of occurrences of 5 in all partitions of n that do not contain 1 as a part. It appears that the sum of five successive terms gives the partition numbers A000041 (see A182703 and A194812).
formula: It appears that A000041(n) = Sum_{j=1..5} a(n+j), n >= 0.
program: (Sage) A206555 = lambda n: sum(list(p).count(5) for p in Partitions(n) if 1 not in p)
xref: Column 5 of A182703 and of A194812.
results.author: _Omar E. Pol_, Feb 09 2012
